DocumentComment: <text>Hand-curated SBOM for dicom-fuzzer 1.11.0. Models the
slim-manual philosophy: only lists components a scanner cannot see (vendored
binaries, statically linked libraries). Direct PyPI dependencies declared in
pyproject.toml are deliberately omitted because Syft already finds them.
See docs/WORKFLOW.md for the curator's full guide.</text>

